# System Monitoring Web App

This project provides system monitoring information via an `/htop` endpoint. The endpoint displays real-time system status, including:

- **Name**: Utkarsh Singh
- **System Username**: codespace
- **Server Time**: 2025-02-20 16:10:23 IST
- **Top Command Output**

## Live Endpoint

Once deployed in a GitHub Codespace, access the `/htop` endpoint:
```
https://<your-github-username>-5000.app.github.dev/htop
```

## Repository Link

[GitHub Repository](https://github.com/yourname/htop-app)

## Technologies Used

- Python
- Flask
- Linux Commands
- GitHub Codespaces

