## Setup Instructions

### 1. Clone the Repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourname/htop-app.git
cd htop-app
```

### 2. Install Dependencies
```bash
pip install flask
```

### 3. Run the Application
```bash
python app.py
```

### 4. Access the Endpoint
After running the server, open the following URL in your browser:
```
http://localhost:5000/htop
```

## Deployment on GitHub Codespaces
1. Start a new Codespace.
2. Install dependencies using `pip install flask`.
3. Run `python app.py`.
4. Expose port **5000** and make it **public**.
5. Access the app using `https://<your-github-username>-5000.app.github.dev/htop`.




